      "title": "60 lakh registered for the National Fuel License",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Information Technology Agency states that 6 million people have registered for the National Fuel Licence. The National Fuel License was introduced to distribute fuel on a quota basis.",
        "The Ministry of Power and Energy has introduced this fuel licensing system to Information Technology Agency, Dialog Import and Millennium IT. The company was created together."
